    title="Start consistently crushing your goals today with BellSkill."
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Step 1: <span class="font-medium">Define Your Fitness Goals</span>',
        description:
          'Begin by clearly defining your fitness goals. Whether you aim to increase strength, improve endurance, or simply maintain overall health, establishing clear objectives will guide your journey with BellSkill.',
        icon: 'tabler:ballpen',
      },
      {
        title: 'Step 2: <span class="font-medium">Customize Your Workouts</em>',
        description:
          "Utilize the app's features to tailor your workouts to align with your goals and preferences. Choose from a variety of weight configurations, exercise options, and interval settings to create a personalized training regimen that suits your needs.",
        icon: 'tabler:adjustments',
      },
      {
        title: 'Step 3: <span class="font-medium">Track Your Progress</span>',
        description:
          "Take advantage of the app's comprehensive tracking tools to monitor your performance over time. Review your reps, volume, and perceived exertion levels after each workout to gain valuable insights into your progress and areas for improvement.",
        icon: 'tabler:activity',
      },
      {
        title: 'Step 4: <span class="font-medium">Stay Consistent</span>',
        description:
          'Consistency is key to achieving lasting results. Commit to regular workouts using BellSkill, and aim to progressively challenge yourself by gradually increasing intensity, volume, or difficulty as your fitness improves.',
        icon: 'tabler:award',
      },
      {
        title: 'Step 5: <span class="font-medium">Listen to Your Body</span>',
        description:
          "Pay attention to your body's signals and adjust your training accordingly. Use the post-workout RPE feature to gauge your exertion levels and assess your recovery needs. Remember to prioritize rest and recovery to prevent burnout and optimize performance.",
        icon: 'tabler:body-scan',
      },
    ]}
